[ATV Purist Up+L1/Up+R1 Off]
author=47iscool
description=These codes will let you always drive a certain vehicle in ANY race. Codes MUST be disabled for the P2P/sprint races immediately before you hit start game or it will freeze during loading. Don't worry though you will still have whatever you picked on the selection screen.

I would only recommended using two vehicle type modifiers at once because these codes use a good bit of memory and slowdowns may occur if three or more enabled but hey it's your choice.
