[Disable/Enable Crash Timer L1+X/R1+X]
author=47iscool
description=This code is for those who like crashing on purpose, basically this will let you see the entire crash without the timer stopping it and your driver will not be able to get on his/her vehicle until you disable the code. Works for opponents too. 
