[Stop/Start All Vehicles L3/R2]
author=47iscool
description=Yet another code for those who like crashing, not suggested for those who are trying to win an event. It freezes all vehicles
and even though you're froze your speed will keep gaining. If you use it for about 10 seconds then disable it you will slam the ground like how the DBZ characters are slammed into buildings,rock etc. If used before the race starts and after you will be levitating upwards. If you use the Invulnerable code with an ATV or Bike or the truck or buggy you will be slammed then go flying and spinning into the air.
patch=1,EE,D0896D82,extended,0000FFFD
patch=1,EE,2030E7D8,extended,00000000
patch=1,EE,D0896D82,extended,0000FDFF
patch=1,EE,2030E7D8,extended,0C0C0A5E

[Stupid/Normal AI L1+L2/R1+R2]
author=47iscool
description=Makes the opponents constantly steer right and run off the track. You will need to disable the code whenever the AI temporarily takes control of your vehicle such as the P2P (aka sprint) races then turn it back on once you have control of your vehicle.
patch=1,EE,D0896D82,extended,0000FAFF
patch=1,EE,20414A1C,extended,54440004
patch=1,EE,D0896D82,extended,0000F5FF
patch=1,EE,20414A1C,extended,4600A002

[Timer is disabled, press R3 to start it ]
author=47iscool
description=Re-enable it after obtaining desired score, best used for freestyle events. Will also need to start it so the gate will let down on normal events.
patch=1,EE,2024025C,extended,00000000
patch=1,EE,D0896D82,extended,0000FFFB
patch=1,EE,2024025C,extended,0C08FFC8

